Your Super Safe Bedroom

	Your Super Safe bedroom has been especially designed for you 
by Your Glorious Hero Teddy Kennedy.

	The Super Safe bedroom features a no profile, super posture, 
back supporting, super safe, adult single size model T, non 
staining mattress by Simmons, The world renown leader of 
manufacturing super safe juvenile furniture of the past. This no 
profile, super posture, back supporting, super safe, adult single 
size model T, non staining mattress by Simmons, uses no dangerous 
frame and needs no dangerous headboard. It is made from non 
toxic, non flammable, un breakable materials that are 
environmentally safe. There are no dangerous pillows or sheets 
that could cause you to accidentally suffocate.

	The Super Safe Bedroom is decorated in the same eyerest 
green ceilings and walls and carpeted with super safe earth tone 
green carpet by ACME. The Super Safe Bedroom is equipped with the 
required tannoy, surveillance cameras, super safe flat wall 
screen TV and computer terminal.

	A picture of Your Glorious Hero Teddy Kennedy is on the wall 
for your enjoyment.

	All people in the Panic Society are required to get their 
eight hours of sleep. They must be in bed by 10PM and rise and 
shine at 6AM.

	You are closely monitored while in your Super Safe Bedroom 
so that Your Glorious Leaders of the Panic Society can rest 
assured that you are behaving yourself morally.

